      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:5:6",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنِ الرَّجُلِ يُقْتَلُ فِي الشَّهْرِ الْحَرَامِ مَا دِيَتُهُ قَالَ دِيَةٌ وَ ثُلُثٌ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Kuleyb Al Asady who said, ",
          "‘I asked Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> about the man who kill during the Sacred Month, what is its wergild?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘A wergild and a one-third (of it in addition)’."
        ]
      }
